    <item>
      <title>经过数周的争论，德国执政联盟敲定 2025 年预算协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/german-coalition-seals-2025-budget-deal-after-weeks-of-wrangling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国执政联盟就明年的预算和刺激经济的新措施达成了一项延期的协议，结束了数周的争论。此前，争论引发了人们对三党联盟执政能力的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/german-coalition-seals-2025-budget-deal-after-weeks-of-wrangling</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 04:42:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普呼吁与拜登进行“无限制”总统辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/trump-calls-for-no-holds-barred-presidential-debate-with-biden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普在 Facebook 上的一篇帖子中表示：“让我们再进行一次辩论，但这一次，没有任何限制——只有我们两个人在台上，进行一场全民讨论。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/trump-calls-for-no-holds-barred-presidential-debate-with-biden</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 04:35:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默如何出乎意料地帮助工党重新掌权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/how-keir-starmer-defied-expectations-to-lift-labour-back-to-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在英国大选投票开始前夕，基尔·斯塔默抽出时间回顾了四年半前成为工党领袖以来取得的进步。当时，工党正遭受百年历史上最惨痛的失败之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/how-keir-starmer-defied-expectations-to-lift-labour-back-to-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 04:16:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰里米·亨特保住议会席位，避免“波蒂略”冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/jeremy-hunt-keeps-seat-in-parliament-avoiding-portillo-shock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣杰里米·亨特在英国大选中保住了议会席位，避免了失败，否则他的名字将永远与保守党的溃败联系在一起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/jeremy-hunt-keeps-seat-in-parliament-avoiding-portillo-shock</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 04:04:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙首相夫人将在有争议的刑事调查中作证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/spanish-prime-minister-sanchez-s-wife-to-testify-in-criminal-inquiry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙首相佩德罗·桑切斯的妻子将于周五出庭作证，作为对其商业交易调查的一部分，该调查已震动了该国政坛数月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/spanish-prime-minister-sanchez-s-wife-to-testify-in-criminal-inquiry</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默领导的工党赢得英国大选，结束了保守党 14 年的统治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/starmer-s-labour-wins-uk-election-ending-14-years-of-tory-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 领导的工党赢得了英国大选，并且有望在选票统计中赢得议会绝大多数席位，这一结果颠覆了里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 领导的保守党垮台后的英国政局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/starmer-s-labour-wins-uk-election-ending-14-years-of-tory-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 03:54:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国大选改革浪潮中奈杰尔·法拉奇赢得下议院席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/nigel-farage-wins-parliament-seat-amid-reform-uk-election-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国脱欧顾问奈杰尔·法拉奇在第八次竞选中赢得了议会席位，这为这位民粹主义改革英国党领袖提供了一个新的平台，以推翻英国政坛传统的保守党和工党双头垄断格局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/nigel-farage-wins-parliament-seat-amid-reform-uk-election-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 02:36:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以下是英国保守党大人物落选的统计数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-election-latest-list-of-conservative-cabinet-ministers-and-others-who-lost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在英国政坛，现任内阁部长在选举中落败的情况极为罕见，以至于 1997 年保守党国防部长早早落败被称为保守党的“波蒂略时刻”。保守党在进入今年的选举时担心，他们可能会在一夜之间遭遇数次失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/uk-election-latest-list-of-conservative-cabinet-ministers-and-others-who-lost</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 02:27:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大批准嘉能可煤炭交易，泰克计划回购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/glencore-s-teck-coal-unit-deal-is-said-to-near-canada-approval</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大已批准嘉能可公司（Glencore Plc）以 69 亿美元收购泰克资源有限公司（Teck Resources Ltd.）的冶金煤业务，后者宣布回购 20 亿美元股票并承诺提高铜产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/glencore-s-teck-coal-unit-deal-is-said-to-near-canada-approval</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 23:38:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国工党获胜，股指期货上涨，英镑持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/pound-steady-as-labour-projected-to-win-majority-in-uk-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国工党赢得议会多数席位后，英国股指期货上涨，英镑维持近期涨势，这赋予了其履行更大经济稳定承诺的明确权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/pound-steady-as-labour-projected-to-win-majority-in-uk-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 21:08:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
